3
00:00:13,536 --> 00:00:17,856
♪Painting realms, clouds in palm,
my brushwork for you♪

4
00:00:18,048 --> 00:00:22,112
♪Light and shadow overlap
my name across time and space♪

5
00:00:22,272 --> 00:00:25,960
