♪Arms spread wide,
falling through heaven and earth♪

7
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:33,280
♪The rhythm of breath and heartbeat♪

8
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:38,464
♪A meeting of the souls♪

9
00:00:39,168 --> 00:00:43,424
♪Through shifting seas and lands,
I'd know you still♪

10
